  "remarks": "In his former capacity as so-called “Head of the Luhansk Central Election Commission” he was responsible for organising the so-called “elections” of 2 Nov 2014 in the “Luhansk People's Republic”. These “elections” were in breach of Ukrainian law and therefore illegal. Between Oct 2015 and Dec 2017 so-called “Minister of Justice” of the “Luhansk People's Republic”.",
